column5: NSPR From 10k shares to 200 Do I sell now and lose 17 bills or do I hold hoping for an increase vs maybe losing 23 bills sigh

NSPR Very soon folks imo That spike yesterday isnt even the real run Its been consolidating around 32s and for a company with cash on hand and low float good pr will fly this to 5 minimum Patience is a virtue For bag holders this is great opportunity to average down
